{
  "2198400": {
    "name": "Yes Comrade",
    "steam_appid": 2198400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/879899fa28dd3745df21fb29ab5f5963.avif?t=1767870676\" width=1400 height=2000 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LONG LIVE THE GLORIOUS NATION OF BELEGOVSKA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes Comrade is a 1 - 4 player cooperative survival sandbox where you and your fellow Comrades are re-assigned to a remote sea outpost. Guard the great Belegovskain coastline, process the ships, keep the <strong><i>Supreme Leader</i></strong> happy, and try not to think too hard about what happens on the island…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONSCRIPTED &quot;VOLUNTEERS!&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Congratulations, Comrade! Your application to return home has been rejected. Instead you have been recommended to serve an indefinite period at one of Belegovska's offshore naval defence facilities. Complete your term and return a hero! Failure to meet expectations and you will be <span class=\"bb_strike\">--REDACTED--</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/d089a9f293d1a21396a9812a6ae53464.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/d089a9f293d1a21396a9812a6ae53464.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/d089a9f293d1a21396a9812a6ae53464.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GUARD OUR GREAT SEA BORDER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your outpost is the last line of defence between the glorious nation of Belegovska and the chaotic western world. From your outpost you will:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track ships on the radar and make contact</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Review cargo, crew manifests, and travel logs with our ever evolving policy and laws</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decide who can enter and who will be temporarily detained for a <span class=\"bb_strike\">--REDACTED--</span> period</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every ship requires you to connect using the various transmission frequencies and ensure the laws of our nation are followed. The <strong><i>Supreme Leader</i></strong> trusts you will make the correct choice… or else…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/9a87cc787e56b2049cfa5c30e4f1e147.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/9a87cc787e56b2049cfa5c30e4f1e147.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/9a87cc787e56b2049cfa5c30e4f1e147.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLEAN, DECORATE, OBEY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The previous occupants of the outpost failed to realise the full decorative potential of your new home. In order to remediate this you will need to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear the debris</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restart the generator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase patriotic decor and approved furniture with your hard earned social credits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hang up our glorious propaganda</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn that cold outpost into a building that our national hero Wally would call home</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's amazing what a few posters, some rations and a microwave can do to boost morale when being observed, Comrade…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/7b22f1f1a9a4c5921dfd9e08d94d0ff6.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/7b22f1f1a9a4c5921dfd9e08d94d0ff6.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/7b22f1f1a9a4c5921dfd9e08d94d0ff6.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SERVE THE NUMBERS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Belegovska Intelligence Service (B.I.S) doesn't care how much work you have done - only that our nation stays safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whilst reviewing important cargo and crew manifests, you may hear an unusual jingle; take out your state issued pen and paper and make note of the numbers to later scan them to headquarters to be reviewed. Who knows Comrade... there even may be a bump to your social credits for your troubles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/ecb338874765459ce110eb6f22d88039.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/ecb338874765459ce110eb6f22d88039.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/ecb338874765459ce110eb6f22d88039.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DOCUMENT THE ANOMALIES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your official directive is to guard the sea border; unofficially, you are  the person closest to whatever is happening out there...</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carry your state provisioned trusty polaroid camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snap anything that looks out of place - anomalies can come in many forms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your photos and scan them back to the Centre for Anomaly Research &amp; Extermination (C.A.R.E)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies only seem to last a day and are harmless, others might follow you home, but those are above your paygrade Comrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/be485d7fcad32eac906afdb5aaca47cf.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/be485d7fcad32eac906afdb5aaca47cf.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/be485d7fcad32eac906afdb5aaca47cf.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SERVE WITH UP TO 3 OTHER COMRADES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes Comrade is an experience built for up to 4 members of communism.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 - 4 player online co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proximity voice chat allows for plenty of ways to commit mutiny and ensure every voice is heard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share out the various tasks and ensure you meet the weekly quota, while discovering all the strange mysteries and happenings on the island</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the way you want to play with your friends; just stay alive while serving and protecting the greatest nation on earth</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/b8f48e0bf8b41669484ace307edd422d.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/b8f48e0bf8b41669484ace307edd422d.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/b8f48e0bf8b41669484ace307edd422d.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run a remote military sea outpost for the glorious nation of Belegovska</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspect, interrogate, and approve any ships based on an daily evolving ruleset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track your quota and gain social credits to buy essentials to survive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean, rebuild, and decorate your outpost with furniture, wallpaper and the finest propaganda</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track strange anomalies and report number stations to keep the state safe</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just remember, Comrade, whatever happens on this outpost you need to ensure our <i><strong>Supreme Leader</strong></i> will log it as a successful venture…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/053dc33e4e7792afa598f4f253b4ca88.poster.avif?t=1767870676\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/053dc33e4e7792afa598f4f253b4ca88.webm?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198400/extras/053dc33e4e7792afa598f4f253b4ca88.mp4?t=1767870676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
